b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Koala AI and Postwise share a solid foundation of core features including Templates, Tone Control. Where Koala AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Long Form and Seo Tools and Multilingual and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Postwise uniquely offers Short Form, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Koala AI holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Postwise scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Koala AI offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $9/mo, compared to Postwise's starting price of $29/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
